dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents the boundaries for public utility districts and munipal utility districts within Placer County, California. This layer is part of a collection of public geospatial datasets produced by the Placer County GIS Division. Placer County Geographic Information Systems. (2020). Utility Districts, Placer County, California, 2020. Placer County Geographic Information Systems. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/fb391vc7350 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
